<h1>INN 2.4 Documentation</h1>

<p>
This documentation is from the current INN 2.4 STABLE branch.  It should
be the most accurate current information for all releases of INN 2.4, but
is only guaranteed to reflect the current STABLE snapshots (which may be
changed over the last INN 2.4 release).
</p>

<p>
Available from this page is all the documentation that has been converted
to POD, but not yet all of INN's documentation.  Much is still only
available in nroff format.  More extensive documentation can be obtained
by downloading the INN 2.4 distribution.
</p>

<p>
Basic documentation:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="readme.html">README</a></li>
<li class="packed"><a href="install.html">INSTALL</a></li>
<li class="packed"><a href="news.html">Changes and upgrade information</a></li>
<li class="packed"><a href="license.html">License information</a></li>
<li class="packed"><a href="contributors.html">Contributors and credits</a></li>
<li class="packed"><a href="checklist.html">Installation checklist</a> (preliminary)</li>
</ul>

<p>
Documentation for developers:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="hacking.html">HACKING</a></li>
<li class="packed"><a href="todo.html">TODO</a></li>
<li class="packed">Configuration parser
<a href="config-design.html">design</a>,
<a href="config-semantics.html">semantics</a>, and
<a href="config-syntax.html">syntax</a></li>
</ul>

<p>
Filtering and authentication hook documentation:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="external-auth.html">nnrpd external authentication hooks</a></li>
<li class="packed"><a href="hook-perl.html">Perl hooks</a></li>
