</ul>

<p>
Configuration files:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="control.ctl.html">control.ctl</a> &mdash; Specify handling of Usenet control messages</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="cycbuff.conf.html">cycbuff.conf</a> &mdash; Configuration for the CNFS storage backend</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="distrib.pats.html">distrib.pats</a> &mdash; Default values for the Distribution header</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="expire.ctl.html">expire.ctl</a> &mdash; Configuration file for article expiration</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="inn.conf.html">inn.conf</a> &mdash; Basic configuration data for INN programs</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="motd.news.html">motd.news</a> &mdash; Message of the day information for readers</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="newsfeeds.html">newsfeeds</a> &mdash; Determine where Usenet articles are sent</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="passwd.nntp.html">passwd.nntp</a> &mdash; Passwords for connecting to remote NNTP servers</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="radius.conf.html">radius.conf</a> &mdash; Configuration for nnrpd RADIUS authenticator</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="readers.conf.html">readers.conf</a> &mdash; Access control and configuration for nnrpd</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="sasl.conf.html">sasl.conf</a> &mdash; SASL configuration for nnrpd</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="subscriptions.html">subscriptions</a> &mdash; Default recommended subscribed groups</li>
</ul>

<p>
Primary daemons and utilities to start them:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="innd.html">innd</a> &mdash; Core daemon for accepting and storing articles</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="inndstart.html">inndstart</a> &mdash; Bind to appropriate ports and start innd</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="nnrpd.html">nnrpd</a> &mdash; NNTP reader server</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="rc.news.html">rc.news</a> &mdash; Start or stop INN daemons</li>
</ul>

<p>
Data files:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="active.html">active</a> &mdash; List of newsgroups carried by the server</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="active.times.html">active.times</a> &mdash; List of local creation times of newsgroups</li>
</ul>

<p>
Outgoing feeds:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="send-uucp.html">send-uucp</a> &mdash; Send Usenet articles via UUCP</li>
</ul>

<p>
Article posting utilities:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="inews.html">inews</a> &mdash; Post an article to the local news server</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="mailpost.html">mailpost</a> &mdash; Feed an e-mail message into a newsgroup</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="pullnews.html">pullnews</a> &mdash; Pull news from one news server and feed it to another</li>
</ul>

<p>
Overview method documentation:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="ovdb.html">OVDB</a></li>
</ul>

<p>
User utilities:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="convdate.html">convdate</a> &mdash; Convert time and date strings and numbers</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="fastrm.html">fastrm</a> &mdash; Quickly remove a list of files</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="grephistory.html">grephistory</a> &mdash; Query the INN history database</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="innconfval.html">innconfval</a> &mdash; Get configuration parameters from inn.conf</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="inndf.html">inndf</a> &mdash; Report free disk, inodes, and overview space</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="innupgrade.html">innupgrade</a> &mdash; Upgrade INN configuration files</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="simpleftp.html">simpleftp</a> &mdash; Rudimentary FTP client</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="sm.html">sm</a> &mdash; Command-line interface to the INN storage manager</li>
</ul>

<p>
Expiration and maintenance utilities:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="expireover.html">expireover</a> &mdash; Perform all overview-driven expiration</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="makehistory.html">makehistory</a> &mdash; Rebuild the history and overview databases</li>
</ul>

<p>
Special article processing:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="ninpaths.html">ninpaths</a> &mdash; Report Usenet Path statistics</li>
</ul>

<p>
Support utilities:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="innmail.html">innmail</a> &mdash; Simple mail sending program</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="perl-nocem.html">perl-nocem</a> &mdash; NoCeM-on-spool implementation</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="pgpverify.html">pgpverify</a> &mdash; Cryptographically verify Usenet control messages</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="sendinpaths.html">sendinpaths</a> &mdash; Send Usenet Path statistics via e-mail</li>
</ul>

<p>
Authentication programs:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="auth_krb5.html">auth_krb5</a> &mdash; nnrpd Kerberos v5 authenticator</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="auth_smb.html">auth_smb</a> &mdash; nnrpd SMB authenticator</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="ckpasswd.html">ckpasswd</a> &mdash; nnrpd password authenticator</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="domain.html">domain</a> &mdash; nnrpd domain resolver</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="ident.html">ident</a> &mdash; nnrpd ident resolver</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="radius.html">radius</a> &mdash; nnrpd RADIUS password authenticator</li>
</ul>

<p>
OVDB overview support utilities:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="ovdb_init.html">ovdb_init</a> &mdash; Prepare OVDB database for use</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="ovdb_monitor.html">ovdb_monitor</a> &mdash; Periodic OVDB database maintenance</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="ovdb_server.html">ovdb_server</a> &mdash; OVDB overview helper server</li>
<li class="packed"><a href="ovdb_stat.html">ovdb_stat</a> &mdash; Display information from the OVDB database</li>
</ul>

<p>
Tradindexed overview support utilities:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="tdx-util.html">tdx-util</a> &mdash; Tradindexed overview manipulation utility</li>
</ul>

<p>
Support library documentation:
</p>

<ul>
<li class="packed"><a href="libauth.html">nnrpd resolver and authenticator library</a></li>
